For overall design, refer to docs/plan.md.
For detailed design, refer to docs/architecture.md.
For progress tracking, refer to docs/milestone.md.
After completing work, update docs/milestone.md.
If design changes occur during development, update docs/architecture.md.
Before committing changes, ensure that `cargo check`, `cargo fmt`, and `cargo clippy` pass successfully.
All code changes must follow Test-Driven Development: write tests first, make them pass, then refactor.
If you encounter the same failure twice, try a different approach or solution strategy.
Follow functional programming paradigm practices.
Strictly adhere to Test-Driven Development principles.